    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit brief for a high school debate prep. Could you expand on that? Specifically, can you go deeper into the legal and philosophical arguments regarding the \"rule of law\" and the social contract aspect of border control? My students need to be able to present these points with real depth and sophistication so they don't look like they're just reciting slogans.",
